tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All measured parameters are within normal limits except for a markedly low HbA1c (2.9%), which may suggest recent hypoglycemia, anemia, or altered red cell turnover. Correlation with clinical context and further evaluation for possible underlying causes is recommended. No evidence of renal or electrolyte disturbances.
